<table border="2" width="450" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<td width="450" ><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2"><b>When Traveling long distances, use this....</b></td><tr>
<td width="450" ><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;When you are traveling a long distance, say you want to get from kelethin to kaladim, just hit the num lock to keep running with out holding down the arrow key.

Falden</td>
</table>
</center><br>
