<td width="450" ><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;HotKey your Spellbook	
Most of us know you can left click and hold on a spell and drop to a hot key. Most of us do not know that you can hotkey your spellbook! Hit F10 to change your view to a view where you can click your "Spells" button. Left click and hold your "Spells" button and drop into an avaialable HotKey slot. Voila! Faster access to that meditate button!

