<td width="450" ><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I have learned (even though still a newbie) Thatr the LOC command can save you hours of time especially when locating your body or itmes that you have hidden in the world.  When your in combat or otherwise type "/loc" to get your location.  EQ is huge, so use it if your unsure where you are.</td>
