<td width="450" ><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;If you want to lift just one of a stack of items, hold down the control key while left clicking on a stack of items.  Just one will be picked up on your pointer.  Great for saving time and wrist strain while tailoring or smithing!  Zorag</td>
