<td width="450" ><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Set your price, and don't sell for too much below it.  I've sold five Bloodforge hammers, all for 35pp and up, even though everyone insisted it was too high.  Someone ALWAYS needs something.  Supply and demand.  You supply it, and demand whatever you want.  :)  And haggle.  Always haggle.

Praetorian</td>
