<table border="2" width="450" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<td width="450" ><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2"><b>Skills to work on while medding</b></td><tr>
<td width="450" ><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Meditating is BORING. What can you do to make better use of this time? Several skills can be done during meditation: Sense Heading, Foraging(wont succeed, but can increase skill), Fishing(will succeed), Tailoring, Baking(with a spit), presumably any other trade skill. I like to cast my line, catch a fish, cast again, cook a fish roll and so on, all while medding.</td>
</table>
</center><br>
